text: Anastasiya Meshcheryakova (August 16, 2011 – February 29, 2016) was a 4-year old Russian girl who was murdered and beheaded on 29 February 2016 in Moscow by her Uzbek nanny, Gulchehra Boboqulova, who had been looking after her for three years.Убийство ребёнка в Москве: ход расследования и реакция общественностиПолиция задержала у метро в Москве женщину с отрезанной головой ребёнка ==References== Category:2011 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Murder in 2016 Category:Murdered children Category:2010s in Russia Category:2010s murders in Europe
title: Murder of Anastasiya Meshcheryakova
